3. IMPLEMENTATION SUMMARY
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  RerankerConfig:           @Bean("rerankerRestClient") RestClient with baseUrl from flowforge.tei.reranker-url (default http://localhost:8083).
  CrossEncoderReranker:      POST /rerank with RerankRequest(query, texts, return_text); deserialize List<RerankResult>(index, score, text); sort by score desc, limit topK; timer flowforge.reranker.latency; rerankDocuments() maps Document.getText(), then restores docs with reranker_score in metadata.
  ResilientReranker:         @CircuitBreaker(name="reranker") @Retry(name="reranker") rerank(); fallbackRerank sorts by metadata "score" (bi-encoder), limit topK.
  RerankerHealthIndicator:   GET /health on rerankerRestClient; Health.up() withDetail model BAAI/bge-reranker-v2-m3.
  application-reranker.yml:  resilience4j circuitbreaker (sliding-window 10, failure-rate 50%, wait 30s) and retry (max 3, 500ms, ResourceAccessException).

